Third Department,

March, 1955.

(March 9, 1955.) In the Matter of the Claim of William C. Aldrich, Appellant, against Central Markets, Inc., et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, by default. Present — Foster, P. J., Bergan, Halpern, Imrie and Zeller, JJ.
